(23, 1, '2018-06-22 05:22:20', '2018-06-22 05:22:20', '<b>Front</b>-<b>end</b> and back-<b>end</b> are terms used to characterize program interfaces and services relative to the initial user of these interfaces and services. (The \"user\" may be a human being or a program.) A \"<b>front</b>-<b>end</b>\" application is one that application users interact with directly.', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-22 05:22:20', '2018-06-22 05:22:20', '', 15, 'http://localhost/working%20area/learning/index.php/2018/06/22/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
